165
00:08:13,430 --> 00:08:14,990
Good question, James.

166
00:08:14,990 --> 00:08:16,979
In a way, that’s already happening.

167
00:08:16,979 --> 00:08:19,669
That is, cheap manufacturing is moving out
of China

168
00:08:19,669 --> 00:08:22,550
